},
{
"type":"heading",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
"Don't Be Tricked"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"7a4c2f",
"children":[
"Right-sided colonic ischemia may be the harbinger of AMI caused by involvement of the superior mesenteric artery and requires CTA or MRA."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
